    "798:241": "ramyaṃ tu ḍākinīcakraṃ svādhiṣṭhānaṃ mahādbhutam |",
    "798:242": "yadudeti kṣaṇenaiva gurupādaprasādataḥ ||",
    "798:243": "sarvabuddhasamāyogaḍākinījālasamvare śrīvajrasattva saṃyogakalpa dvitīyo (ye)",
    "798:244": "'pyuktaṃ bhagavatā",
    "798:245": "svādhiṣṭhānād bhavatyeva sarvabuddhasamāgama itī |",
    "798:246": "bodhicittaṃ sadāraktaṃ duḥkhanirvatihetukam |",
    "798:247": "anyathā hi na buddhatvaṃ kalpa saṃkhyeyakoṭibhiḥ ||",
    "798:248": "tāttvikā durlabhā loke anye vā''varṇa (varaṇā)thitāḥ (naḥ) |",
    "798:249": "āvaraṇaprahāṇāddhi yoginaste'tidurlabhāḥ ||",
    "798:250": "tathā coktamāryavasubandhupādaiḥ",
    "798:251": "'' āvaraṇaparicchedo hi bodhiḥ |",
    "798:252": "trīṇyāvaraṇāni kuśalānutpādaḥ ,",
    "798:253": "aparipūrṇasambhāratā ,",
    "798:254": "amanasikāratā ca |",
    "798:255": "tatha saddharma agocaram ,",
    "798:256": "lābhasatkārapūjāyāṃ gauravam ,",
    "798:257": "sarveṣu akāruṇyaṃ ceti | ''",
    "798:258": "punaścoktam ''apratiṣṭhitanirvāṇamapyāvaranaṃ bodhisattvagotrāṇām '' iti |",
    "798:259": "tathā mokṣābhilāśo (ṣo)",
    "798:260": "'pi bodhisatvānāmāvaraṇamiti vistaraḥ |",
    "798:261": "tathā ratnacūḍādimahāyānasūtre coktaṃ bhagavatā ''sarvākāravaropetā śūnyatā bhāvanīya yoginā '' iti |",
    "798:262": "tasyāmapi sarvākāravaropetāyāṃ śūnyatāyāṃ yadyabhiniveśaḥ syāt ,",
    "798:263": "idameva tattvasāramityākāreṇa ,",
    "798:264": "so'pi dṛṣṭernarakagamanaheturiti |",
    "798:265": "tathā coktam ''yaśca śānta matiḥ sattvadharmasamatāṃ jānāti ,",
    "798:266": "na sa dharmān vā adharmān va abhiniveśa (viśe) ta |",
    "798:267": "anabhiniveśo dharmāṇāmarthaḥ |",
    "798:268": "yaścārthamatyete (ti)",
    "798:269": "sa evāsya mahānarthaḥ '' iti |",
    "798:270": "evaṃ cet , mokṣārambho vyarthaḥ syāt |",
    "798:271": "etad bhagavato hṛdayo (yaṃ)",
    "798:272": "nābhijñā (jña)",
    "798:273": "sya vacanam |",
    "798:274": "bandhamokṣa ityudbhāvanā saṃvṛtyā vā tat tattvato na mokṣa iti |",
    "798:275": "tathā coktam",
    "798:276": "baddho na mucyate loke abaddho naiva mucyate |",
    "798:277": "baddhābaddhavinirmukto nānyo [vā] stoha tattvataḥ ||",
    "798:278": "tathā coktam",
    "798:279": "tasmāda [na] nyathābhāvaḥ svabhāvo yadi (na ) vidyate |",
    "798:280": "kathaṃ syādanyathābhāvā (vo)",
    "798:281": "bhāvaścennaiva vidyate ||",
    "798:282": "svavikrāmiṇaḥ pṛcchāyāṃ coktam “ ye ca svavikrāmino (ṇo)",
    "798:283": "bodhisattvā mahāsattvā na vikalpayanti ,",
    "798:284": "astyasau bodhirnām padārtho yasyārthāvayavamudyukto dūre teṣāṃ bodhisattva [ḥ] |",
    "798:285": "visaṃvādayanti te sadevamānuṣāsura lokaṃ bodhisattvā na ca vistaraḥ |",
    "798:286": "ityevaṃ nādaret |",
    "798:287": "asti nāsti cobhayaṃ pratisi (ṣi)",
    "798:288": "ddhaṃ bhagavatā bhāvābhāvavibhā vinā |",
    "798:289": "tathā coktam",
    "798:290": "śūnyatāṃ ye na jānanti na te jānanti nirvṛtam |",
    "798:291": "tasmāddhi śunyatā jñeyā bhāvābhāvavibhāvinā ||",
    "798:292": "uktaṃ ca",
    "798:293": "śubhāśubhavikalpānāṃ santaticchedalalakṣaṇā |",
    "798:294": "śūnyatā gaditā buddhainanyit (nyā vai)",
    "798:295": "śunyatā matā || iti |",
    "798:296": "tathācoktam",
    "798:297": "śūnyatā sarvadṛṣṭīnāṃ proktā niḥśaraṇa jinaiḥ |",
    "798:298": "yeṣāṃ tu śūnyatādṛṣṭistānasādhyān babhāṣire || iti |",
    "798:299": "gurubhakti [ra] to nityaṃ nityaṃ ca karuṇāśayaḥ |",
    "798:300": "mantrapūjāva (ra)",
    "798:301": "to nityaṃ siddhayatyeva na saṃśayaḥ ||",
    "798:302": "ato bodhiṃ parāṃ yānti kālenaivādisādhanam |",
    "798:303": "kuśalamutpādayitavyaṃ gurupāramparyavekṣaṇena || iti ||",
    "798:304": "tathā coktam vajrasattvasaṃbuddhai nanyit (nyā)",
    "798:305": "śūnyatā gaditā |",
    "798:306": "(śunyatā) ato hi samantabhadrasya deśanā",
    "798:307": "ākāśayava yogena gṛhlanti jñānasāgarāḥ |",
    "798:308": "atha vajradharo rājā mahāsukha vivardhanam ||",
    "798:309": "samaya deśayet sarva buddhatvaphaladāyakam |",
    "798:310": "sukhairhṛṣṭai stathā nṛtyairgītavādyaivikurvaṇaiḥ ||",
    "798:311": "gandhamālyavilepanaistu vidyārājaḥ prasiddhayati |",
    "798:312": "yathā sukhaṃ sukhaṃ vādye yathārucitaceṣṭītam ||",
    "798:313": "yathāhāravihāro'pi siddhayate paramākṣaram |",
    "798:314": "khānapānaprayoga (gai)",
    "798:315": "stu divyālaṅkārabhūṣaṇaiḥ ||",
    "798:316": "siddhayate paramaṃ tattvaṃ dinenaikena coditaḥ |",
    "798:317": "nityaṃ svasamayaḥ sādhyo nityaṃ pūjyāstathāgatāḥ ||",
    "798:318": "nityaṃ ca guravedeyaṃ tasmād buddha (tva) samo guruḥ |",
    "798:319": "yathā vairocano nāthastathā vajradharo guruḥ ||",
    "798:320": "yathākāśo mahārā (gaṃ)",
    "798:321": "jo vajradharmo mahāmuniḥ |",
    "798:322": "samantarājo yathā nāthastathācāryaḥ pragīyate ||",
    "798:323": "tasmātsarvaprayatnena vajrācārya mahāgurum |",
    "798:324": "pracchannavarakānyāsaṃ nāvamanyāt kadācana ||",
    "798:325": "punarapyuktaṃ vajrapañjare",
    "798:326": "gurośchāyāṃ na laṅghayed [guru] patnīṃ ca pādukā [m] |",
    "798:327": "ye laṅghayanti sammohāt te narāḥ kṣuradhāriṇaḥ ||",
    "798:328": "sva (su) siddho'pi yadā śiṣyo gurorājñāṃ na (tu) laṅghayet |",
    "798:329": "iha loke bhavetkuṣṭhaḥ (ṣṭhī)",
    "798:330": "paraloke narakaṃ vaset ||",
    "798:331": "māyā śāṭhayaprayogeṇa mithyābhaktiprakāśanāt |",
    "798:332": "kṣayakuṣṭhamahārogī jāyate narakādiṣu ||",
    "798:333": "evaṃ matvā sadā śiṣyo gurorbhaktiparāyaṇaḥ |",
    "798:334": "sādhayet vipulāṃ siddhi gurorājñāṃ praṇayata (jñāprapālanāt) ||",
    "798:335": "|| iti ḍākinījālasaṃvararahasyaṃ samāptam ||"
}